        A constructor used to create an AVElement instance.
        Parameters:
        description - Indicates the description of a media item.
        flags - Specifies whether the media item can be played and scanned. The flags are as follows:
        • AVELEMENT_FLAG_SCANNABLE
        • AVELEMENT_FLAG_PLAYABLE
